Title: Authorizes the city of Long Beach to alienate and discontinue the use of certain parklands
Summary: Authorizes the city of Long Beach to alienate and discontinue the use of certain parklands to EW Offshore Wind Transport Corporation for the purpose of constructing, maintaining and operating a subterranean conduit and electrical distribution cable system, together with subterranean transition joint bays and link boxes, and appurtenances thereto, under city of Long Beach parkland.
ActClause: AN ACT in relation to authorizing the city of Long Beach to alienate and discontinue the use of certain parklands
